javadoc: Array of long[] that grows as needed.

methods.name: put
methods.comment:
Puts the given long array in the long array array at
 the given index

methods.name: get
methods.comment: Returns the long array at the given index in the LongArrayArray.

return.comment:
The long array value at the given index. An empty array will
 be returned for any index not initialized to
 another value.

methods.name: remove
methods.comment: Removes the long array at the given index

params.name: index
params.comment: index of the array to be removed

methods.javadoc: Returns the index of the last non-null or non-zero element in the array.
methods.name: getLastNonEmptyIndex
methods.comment: Returns the index of the last non-null or non-zero element in the array.

name: LongArrayArray
comment: Array of long[] that grows as needed.
